    <item>
      <title>特朗普回归或将再次颠覆美国外交政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-s-return-looks-to-upend-us-foreign-policy-once-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫，誓言要颠覆与盟友和敌人的关系，而他这次面临的限制与上次“美国优先”政策的制约却有所减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-s-return-looks-to-upend-us-foreign-policy-once-again</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 14:49:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选重燃通胀风险 债券价格创 2020 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/us-bonds-slide-most-since-pandemic-as-trump-renews-inflation-bet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债收益率飙升——30 年期国债收益率创下 2020 年 3 月全球套现浪潮以来的最大涨幅——因为投资者再次押注唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫将推高通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/us-bonds-slide-most-since-pandemic-as-trump-renews-inflation-bet</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 12:45:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普准备放松管制，高盛、花旗股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/goldman-citi-soar-on-hopes-of-less-tax-regulation-under-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者押注唐纳德·特朗普将兑现降低税收和减少银行业监管的承诺，花旗集团、摩根大通和高盛集团等美国银行的股价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/goldman-citi-soar-on-hopes-of-less-tax-regulation-under-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 11:56:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普宣誓开战 乌克兰债券价格在获胜后上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-s-pledges-on-war-send-ukraine-s-bonds-rallying-after-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普再次当选美国总统后，他承诺加快努力结束与俄罗斯的战争，乌克兰的美元债券价格随之上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-s-pledges-on-war-send-ukraine-s-bonds-rallying-after-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 10:33:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克押注特朗普有望带来回报，特斯拉股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/tesla-soars-as-musk-s-all-in-bet-on-trump-seen-reaping-rewards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司 (Tesla Inc.) 股价在美国交易中上涨了 15%，因为投资者押注埃隆马斯克 (Elon Musk) 运营的这家汽车制造商将成为唐纳德特朗普 (Donald Trump) 重返白宫的最大受益者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/tesla-soars-as-musk-s-all-in-bet-on-trump-seen-reaping-rewards</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 09:02:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选提振美元 大宗商品下跌 贸易局势紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走强以及唐纳德·特朗普担任总统期间可能出现的贸易争端将削弱原材料在全球市场上的吸引力，大宗商品价格普遍下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:25:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选，标普 500 指数创历史新高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市创下历史新高，债券收益率飙升，美元出现自 2020 年以来的最大涨幅，投资者关注唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫以及他的政策对市场的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:05:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>超微因退市风险隐现而前景黯淡，股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/super-micro-slips-on-sales-outlook-that-falls-short-of-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[超微电脑公司 (Super Micro Computer Inc.) 股价周三暴跌，此前这家服务器制造商发布了令人失望的销售预测，且未能公布提交上一财年官方财务报表的时间表。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/super-micro-slips-on-sales-outlook-that-falls-short-of-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 21:35:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
